{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过实验了解影响</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">滑动摩擦力</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大小的因素，进一步了解控制变量法</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在实验中的运用。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">物体处于平衡状态时，拉力等于摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">长木板、带钩木块、砝码、弹簧测力计</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.用弹簧测力计匀速拉动木块，使它沿水平长木板滑动，从而测出木块与长木板之间的滑动摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.改变长木板材质为玻璃，用弹簧测力计匀速拉动木块，测出木块与玻璃之间的滑动摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.改变长木板材质为棉布，用弹簧测力计匀速拉动木块，测出木块与棉布之间的滑动摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.改变长木板材质为毛巾，用弹簧测力计匀速拉动木块，测出木块与毛巾之间的滑动摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.去掉长木板上面所铺物体，在木块上加上砝码，用弹簧测力计匀速拉动木块，测出木块与木板之间的滑动摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">6.去掉砝码，改用木块的侧面与长木板接触，用弹簧测力计匀速拉动木块，测出木块与木板之间的滑动摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">7.改用木块的正面与长木板接触，用弹簧测力计以较快速度匀速拉动木块，测出木块与木板之间的滑动摩擦力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:FZFSJW--GB1-0\">&hellip;&hellip;</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">请把实验现象记录在表格中</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">滑动摩擦力的大小跟接触面所受的压力与接触面的粗糙程度有关，接触面受到的压力越大，接触面越粗糙，滑动摩擦力越大。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.该实验过程利用了控制变量法；</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.摩擦力大小与物体运动速度快慢无关。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}